{
  "stem": "24171.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I know there was the Hungarians going to the front of Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they stopped in our village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a, I don't know, a high rank official in our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We gave one of those bedrooms to give them, and the horses there, and the stable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and my sister across the street, she lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in their house was, you know, [? all ?] [? the way. ?] They took in the Jewish places, because the Jewish people had the houses more to accommodate them and-- and the food.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, they had their own kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they liked the home cooked meals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I know that we had already that time the-- the yellow star, because I had a sister living a little bit further [INAUDIBLE], because the gentleman what he gave the house, he moved to the city, to [?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Mukacheve. ?] And my sister was living there by [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember like a Thursday night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My sister didn't [INAUDIBLE] to bake bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Thursday night, we had to prepare the bread for Friday morning to bake the challahs and the bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was not allowed for me to go to my sister to get what she wants to ask if [INAUDIBLE], and especially after 6 o'clock, or whatever it was, the curfew, was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the guy which was there, he was the-- he was cleaning the [INAUDIBLE] for that big captain, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He stayed in our house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if he went with me, that means that I was allowed to go there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where it start.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was kind of like about--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and they left.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
